OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with some drizzle in
OL,7,Fplaces, especially near the coast.
OL,8,FSome clearer spells developing early
OL,9,Fon Sunday morning. Light easterly
OL,10,Fwinds becoming southerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely dry day with
OL,13,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells. The
OL,14,Fodd isolated shower possible. Feeling
OL,15,Fwarm again.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,18,Fwith showers on Monday, winds
OL,19,Fremaining light. A mix of bright or
OL,20,Fsunny spells and cloud on Tuesday and
OL,21,FWednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
